When Endymion presented MYST to the Nightbreed label with their first collaboration “Death Never Dies”, they knew it was only a matter of time before they would team up again. Skip ahead two years, and here it is: their follow-up collab “See You Again”! Experience the uplifting sensation that can only be found in magical team-ups like this. This’ll definitely get you in the mood for the festival season!

“See You Again“ is now available on Nightbreed Records → http://nightbreed.lnk.to/seeyouagain
